## 总体架构

```text
                 Mobile App

                    |

              API Gateway

                    |

              Backend Core

                    |

 ┌────────────────────────────────┐

 Observation Engine

 Understanding Engine

 Fact Engine

 Timeline Engine

 Report Engine

 └────────────────────────────────┘

                    |

              Data Layer

                    |

 PostgreSQL + Vector Storage

                    |

              LLM Provider
```

